    <title type="text">Hangout with Bill Morris</title>
    <id>https://cartonama.com/2012/hangout-with-bill-morris</id>
    <link href="https://cartonama.com/2012/hangout-with-bill-morris"/>
    <updated>2012-08-28T13:58:06Z</updated>
    <published>2012-09-12T08:12:34Z</published>
    <content type="html">
      &lt;p&gt;Join Bill Morris and other map data enthusiasts in a Google Hangout tonight at 7:30pm IST, 28 August 2012.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bill is principal at &lt;a href=&#34;http://geosprocket.com/&#34; title=&#34;GeoSprocket&#34;&gt;GeoSprocket LLC&lt;/a&gt;, a multifaceted geospatial consulting firm. With over a decade of experience in geographic information science, remote sensing and cartography, he focuses on applying the strength of spatial relationships to real-world challenges in the areas of environmental resource conservation, agricultural management and international development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://plus.google.com/hangouts/_/e4bffe6c2d8a71a305890b7cf9abf2d9b5ba9881?pqs=1&amp;amp;authuser=0&amp;amp;hl=en&#34; title=&#34;Hangout with Bill Morris&#34;&gt;Join the Hangout&lt;/a&gt; directly and post your questions in live chat or if you don&#39;t have a Google+ account you can watch the Hangout &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GdfkC7WFIbs&#34;&gt;live on YouTube&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
